<br>
If you can't count on a +75 spec buff, and your gear isn't chosen for the max +75 bonus to STR, then any caps might not affect you.  There's no obvious answer which racial stats work better once buffs and caps are taken into account, but my Firbolg put his starting points in dex qui and con, as there's porbably not a lot of point in the endgame in haveing a base str over 90. <p>Skorj 
